### Schedules API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/schedules
### Auth: Bearer token required (Clerk JWT)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_clerk_jwt_token_here
@repurposingJobId = replace_with_actual_job_id

### 1. Get optimal posting time (AI-powered)
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules/optimal
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": "video_123",
  "contentType": "video",
  "platform": "instagram",
  "goal": "engagement",
  "timezone": "America/New_York"
}

### Example Response:
### {
###   "recommendedTime": "2025-10-09T14:00:00Z",
###   "alternativeTimes": [
###     "2025-10-09T18:00:00Z",
###     "2025-10-10T09:00:00Z"
###   ],
###   "confidence": 85,
###   "expectedPerformance": {
###     "estimatedEngagement": 250,
###     "estimatedReach": 5000
###   },
###   "reasoning": [
###     "Peak engagement hours for your target audience",
###     "Lower competition during this time slot",
###     "Historical data shows 2x higher reach"
###   ]
### }

### 2. Bulk schedule content
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentIds": ["video_1", "video_2", "video_3", "video_4"],
  "platforms": ["instagram", "tiktok"],
  "brandIds": ["account_insta_1", "account_tiktok_1"],
  "schedulingStrategy": "ai-optimal",
  "staggerMinutes": 60
}

### Example Response:
### {
###   "scheduled": [
###     {
###       "_id": "schedule_1",
###       "contentId": "video_1",
###       "platform": "instagram",
###       "scheduledAt": "2025-10-09T14:00:00Z",
###       "expectedEngagement": 85
###     }
###   ],
###   "failed": []
### }

### Bulk schedule with custom times
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentIds": ["video_1", "video_2"],
  "platforms": ["instagram"],
  "brandIds": ["account_1"],
  "schedulingStrategy": "custom",
  "customTimes": {
    "video_1": "2025-10-09T14:00:00Z",
    "video_2": "2025-10-09T18:00:00Z"
  }
}

### Bulk schedule with even distribution
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentIds": ["post_1", "post_2", "post_3"],
  "platforms": ["instagram"],
  "brandIds": ["account_1"],
  "schedulingStrategy": "evenly-distributed",
  "staggerMinutes": 120
}

### 3. Get schedule calendar
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedules/calendar?start=2025-10-08T00:00:00Z&end=2025-11-08T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Example Response:
### [
###   {
###     "_id": "schedule_1",
###     "contentId": "video_123",
###     "contentType": "video",
###     "platform": "instagram",
###     "scheduledAt": "2025-10-09T14:00:00Z",
###     "status": "pending",
###     "expectedEngagement": 85
###   }
### ]

### 4. Repurpose content (THE MAGIC!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules/repurpose
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": "long_video_123",
  "targetFormats": ["short-video", "story", "carousel", "gif"],
  "settings": {
    "preserveBranding": true,
    "qualityLevel": "high",
    "targetDuration": 30
  }
}

### Example Response:
### {
###   "_id": "repurpose_job_123",
###   "status": "pending",
###   "sourceContentId": "long_video_123",
###   "targetFormats": ["short-video", "story", "carousel", "gif"],
###   "results": [
###     { "format": "short-video", "status": "pending" },
###     { "format": "story", "status": "pending" },
###     { "format": "carousel", "status": "pending" },
###     { "format": "gif", "status": "pending" }
###   ],
###   "progress": 0
### }

### Repurpose with minimal settings
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules/repurpose
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": "video_456",
  "targetFormats": ["short-video", "gif"]
}

### 5. Get repurposing status
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedules/repurpose/{{repurposingJobId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Example Response:
### {
###   "_id": "repurpose_job_123",
###   "status": "completed",
###   "progress": 100,
###   "results": [
###     {
###       "format": "short-video",
###       "status": "completed",
###       "url": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/..."
###     },
###     {
###       "format": "story",
###       "status": "completed",
###       "url": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/..."
###     },
###     {
###       "format": "carousel",
###       "status": "failed",
###       "error": "Image extraction failed"
###     },
###     {
###       "format": "gif",
###       "status": "completed",
###       "url": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/..."
###     }
###   ],
###   "completedAt": "2025-10-08T15:30:00Z"
### }

### Full workflow example
### Step 1: Get optimal time
# @name getOptimalTime
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules/optimal
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": "my_video",
  "contentType": "video",
  "platform": "tiktok",
  "goal": "engagement"
}

### Step 2: Bulk schedule based on optimal times
@recommendedTime = {{getOptimalTime.response.body.recommendedTime}}

POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentIds": ["my_video"],
  "platforms": ["tiktok"],
  "brandIds": ["my_tiktok"],
  "schedulingStrategy": "ai-optimal"
}

### Step 3: Repurpose for other platforms
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules/repurpose
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": "my_video",
  "targetFormats": ["story", "short-video"],
  "settings": {
    "preserveBranding": true,
    "qualityLevel": "high"
  }
}

### Step 4: Check calendar
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedules/calendar?start=2025-10-08T00:00:00Z&end=2025-10-15T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


